question: who win road march in trinidad and tobago
vanilla_rag_result:
The Trinidad and Tobago Road March title has been won by several artists over the years. Notable winners include:

- Lord Kitchener, with eleven wins.
- Super Blue, with ten wins.
- Machel Montano, also with ten wins.
- The Mighty Sparrow, with eight wins.
- Calypso Rose, who won in 1977 and 1978.
- Destra, who won in 2003.
- Fay-Ann Lyons, who is a three-time champion (2003, 2008, 2009).
- Skinny Fabulous, who won in 2019.

These artists are among the most recognized winners of the Road March title in Trinidad and Tobago.
